            * French: {{t+|fr|chaque}}
            * German: {{t+|de|beide}}
            * Greek: {{t+|el|είτε}}
            * Hungarian: {{t+|hu|vagy}}
            * Italian: {{t+|it|ciascuno}}, {{t+|it|entrambi|m-p}}, {{t+|it|ogni}}
            * Latin: {{t|la|alteruter}}
            {{trans-mid}}
            * Norwegian:
            *: Bokmål: {{t+|nb|begge}}
