            ===Conjunction===
            {{en-con}}
            # By or for the [[cause]] that; on this [[account]] that; for the [[reason]] that.
            #: {{ux|en|I hid myself '''because''' I was afraid.}}
            #* {{RQ:Churchill Celebrity|chapter=1|passage=I was about to say that I had known the Celebrity from the
            time he wore kilts. But I see I will have to amend that, '''because''' he was not a celebrity then, nor,
            indeed, did he achieve fame until some time after I left New York for the West.}}
            #*
            {{quote-journal|en|year=2013|month=May-June|author=[http://www.americanscientist.org/authors/detail/katrina-g-claw
            Katrina G. Claw]
            |title=[http://www.americanscientist.org/issues/feature/2013/3/rapid-evolution-in-eggs-and-sperm Rapid
            Evolution in Eggs and Sperm]
            |volume=101|issue=3|magazine={{w|American Scientist}}
            |passage=In plants, the ability to recognize self from nonself plays an important role in fertilization,
            '''because''' self-fertilization will result in less diverse offspring than fertilization with pollen from
            another individual.}}
            #* {{RQ:Maxwell Mirror and the Lamp|chapter=17|passage=“Perhaps it is '''because''' I have been
            excommunicated. It's absurd, but I feel like the Jackdaw of Rheims.”&nbsp; ¶&nbsp;She winced and
            bowed her head. Each time that he spoke flippantly of the Church he caused her pain.}}
            # As is [[known]], [[inferred]], or [[determined]] from the [[fact]] that.
            #: {{ux|en|It must be broken, '''because''' I pressed the button and nothing happened.}}
            #: {{ux|en|I don't think he is a nice person, '''because''' he yells at people for no reason.}}
            # {{lb|en|obsolete}} So that, [[in order]] that. {{defdate|15th|17th c.}}
            #* {{RQ:Burton Melancholy|part=II|section=3|member=2|passage=Simon{{...}}set the house on fire where he was
            born, '''because''' nobody should point at it.}}
