            ===Preposition===
            {{en-prep}}
            # {{lb|en|colloquial|internet slang}} [[on account of|On account of]], [[because of]]. {{defdate|from 20th
            c. or before}}
            #: {{ux|en|He rejected me '''because''' revenge, I guess.}}
            #: {{ux|en|It doesn't work [[because reasons|'''because''' reasons]].}}
