            you. [...] I say [it] wass no use '''for''' spen money. [...] An I say in "So wass I. I see lot of
            sy-pokes fly up an twist off like screw-cork an spit whistle, but I wass'nt able '''for''' get aim on
            him." }}
            #* '''2007''', H. Nigel Thomas, ''Return to Arcadia: A Novel'' (Tsar Publications):
            #*: "She say that when nigger people step out o&#39; they place and start '''for''' rub shoulders
