            ==Latin==
            {{attention|la|please expand}}
            ===Etymology===
            {{root|la|ine-pro|*bʰeh₂-|id=speak}}
            From {{inh|la|itc-pro|*fāōr}}, from {{inh|la|ine-pro|*bʰéh₂ti||to speak}}. It's unclear why the verb is
            [[deponent]].
            ===Pronunciation===
            * {{la-IPA|for}}
            ===Verb===
            {{la-verb|1+.p3inf|for}}, ''defective''
            # I [[speak]], [[talk]], [[say]].
            #: {{syn|la|effor|inquam|oro|aio|dico|alloquor|loquor}}
            ====Conjugation====
            Certain forms were not used in Classical Latin.
            {{la-conj|1+.p3inf|for}}
