            # {{lb|en|philosophy}} Something being indicated that is [[here]]; one of [[these]].
            #* {{quote-book|en|year=2001|author=James G. Lennox|title=Aristotle's Philosophy of
            Biology|page=151|passage=Terms like 'house', 'sphere', 'animal', and 'human' do not refer to other
            '''thises''' distinct from these ones here &mdash; they refer to the sort of thing these ones here
            are.}}
            ===Interjection===
            {{en-interj}}
            # {{lb|en|Internet slang}} {{non-gloss definition|Indicates the speaker's strong [[approval]] or
            [[agreement]] with the previous material.}}
            #: {{ux|en|― I wish trolls could be banned from the forum immediately, without any discussion.<br>―
            '''This'''!}}
            ====Synonyms====
            * {{l|en|+1}}
            * {{l|en|IAWTP}}
            * {{l|en|QFT}}
